reviews.review_text:
Time travel to 1988/correction to source info *Source correction: show was recorded with Sennheiser 421s instead of 441s.

Taped by Mark McCue and Lucien Zaleski.
Transferred, Edited and Mastered by Alex Ford. 

Comment: 

- "Roll Out The Barrel" between tracks d1t04 and d1t05.

Notes:

- Pitch correction performed on Set 02.
- Crossfades applied to smooth out tape pauses.
- Shnid=90776 used to provide both tape flip patches, 0:00-0:44 of Masterpiece and 01:47-01:56 of China Cat.
